thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Fisrt Time user

author: Fisrt Time user
title: Fisrt Time user
text:
Small problem with the software in arranging the pickup of the items. Selected the time and day options and found that they were not displayed on the final screen. Pickup occurred one day early.
Overall prompt and great service at a reasonable price for a first timer.
